sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as SOC Analyst
  participant FE as Next.js Frontend
  participant BE as /api/v1/assistant
  participant CB as context_builder
  participant DB as SQLite + Elasticsearch
  participant AI as AI Provider / LLM
  U->>FE: ask question (optional focus entity)
  FE->>BE: POST message (conversation_id, focus_entity)
  BE->>CB: gather context (investigation/incident/alert/system)
  CB->>DB: read scoped records
  DB-->>CB: context records
  CB-->>BE: grounded context + sources
  BE->>AI: prompt (question + context)
  AI-->>BE: answer + suggested actions
  BE->>DB: persist AssistantMessage (sources_json)
  BE-->>FE: answer + sources + actions
